                <p><app loc="a"><note>sinistroverse</note></app></p>
                <p><app loc="b"><note>read from editor's drawing: probably dextroverse; if sinitroverse, the reading might perhaps be <unclear>ν</unclear>χ<unclear>ι</unclear></note></app></p>
